------Life Cyle Methods 


--  when u run a class component --
few methods get called internally 

Phases of Class Component lifecycle

Mounting  - the html gets attached to the DOM 
   constructor()
   static getDerivedStateFromProps()
   render()
   componentDidMount()


Updating  - when we update the component 
    static getDerivedStateFromProps()
    shouldComponentUpdate() (avoid unnecessary updation DOM)
    getSnapShotBeforeUpdate()
    render()
    componentDidUpdate()

Unmounting
   -- componentWillUnMount
Error Handling 
    --  static getDerivedStateFromError()
    -- componentDidCatch()